Game: Candy Counter
Creator: Koren Lam


I had designed a simple puzzle game which involves identifying the number of candies within 10 seconds. The game generates a random amount of candies depending on the difficulty level chosen. Games that test an individual's short term memory skills are proven to increase long term memory skills if training partakes everyday. 

I had decided to incorporate 2 assignments and create a game altogether using both user feedback and an array of candies